<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_205_r2l6">Lıeber Diecʒ / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒwitracht <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r2l7">als Jr mit <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Babemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> habt / vnd <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> daʒ ew geſagt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r2l10">ſeÿ <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ die <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> mit ſeinen 
