<add><ab facs="#facs_205_line_1576594946131_8627">dıenern </ab></add> <expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd ſtreiffen / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r2l11"><expan>Laʒʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wıſen / daʒ vns ſölıch cʒwitraht nicht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_205_r2l12">lıeb ıſt / vnd <expan>vvolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / daʒ Jr mit <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Babemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
