<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>cʒeit<ex>e</ex>n</expan> nicht getan </del> / . vnd wir <expan>bitt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd getrawen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
